  <name>Perfusor Orders</name>
  <description>MLLP hub: receives HL7 ORM^O01 medication orders from OpenEMR, maps medication name to perfusor number, and writes a JSON order file for the order_executor service to apply via Modbus to the perfusor PLC. Closes the OpenEMR → PLC infusion pump control loop.</description>
